#. Tag: title
#: user-interface.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>User Interface</title>"
msgstr "<title>Uporabniški vmesnik</title>"

#. Tag: primary
#: user-interface.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid "<primary>User Interface</primary>"
msgstr "<primary>Uporabniški vmesnik</primary>"

#. Tag: title
#: user-interface.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid "OFM User Interface"
msgstr "Uporabniški vmesnik OFM"

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:14
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The OFM file manager concept contains <link linkend=\"features\">many "
"features</link> that make them powerful enough to belong among the best file "
"managers today. The interface is simple: left panel, right panel and a "
"command line below. Because of interaction between these three items the "
"file managing will become more efficient."
msgstr ""
"Koncept upravitelja datotek OFM vsebuje <link linkend=\"features\">številne "
"funkcije</link>, zaradi katerih so dovolj zmogljivi, da sodijo med najboljše "
"upravitelje datotek danes. Vmesnik je preprost: leva plošča, desna plošča in "
"ukazna vrstica spodaj. Zaradi interakcije med temi tremi elementi bo "
"upravljanje datotek postalo učinkovitejše."

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you would like to know <ulink url=\"http://www.softpedia.com/reviews/"
"linux/Krusader-Review-18193.shtml\"> how &krusader; works</ulink> you can "
"try it yourself, just install it on your computer. To accept an <ulink url="
"\"http://www.softpanorama.org/OFM/index.shtml\">Orthodox File Manager (OFM)</"
"ulink> like &krusader;, the user needs to get used to <emphasis>new ideas</"
"emphasis> that are actually already 20 years old. If you prefer to waste "
"time and lose a lot of productivity, you can always continue to use one "
"panel file managers that are based on &Windows; Explorer."
msgstr ""
"Če bi radi izvedeli <ulink url=\"http://www.softpedia.com/reviews/linux/"
"Krusader-Review-18193.shtml\"> kako &krusader; deluje</ulink> lahko "
"poskusite sami, samo namestite ga na svoj računalnik. Če želi uporabnik "
"sprejeti <ulink url=\"http://www.softpanorama.org/OFM/index.shtml\">Orthodox "
"File Manager (OFM)</ulink>, kot je &krusader;, se mora navaditi na "
"<emphasis>novo ideje</emphasis>, ki so dejansko stare že 20 let. Če raje "
"izgubljate čas in izgubite veliko produktivnosti, lahko vedno nadaljujete z "
"uporabo upraviteljev datotek na eni plošči, ki temeljijo na &Windows; "
"Raziskovalec."

#. Tag: title
#: user-interface.docbook:33 user-interface.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>&krusader; Main Window</title>"
msgstr "<title>&krusader; Glavno okno</title>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: user-interface.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&krusader; Main Window</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&krusader; Glavno okno</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The User Interface is based on <ulink url=\"http://www.softpanorama.org/OFM/"
"index.shtml\">Orthodox File Manager (OFM)</ulink> paradigm, a 20- year old "
"principle that has proven its bones. It is known as simple, easy and "
"powerful. In the following sections we will cover the basic functions of "
"each part with the exception of:"
msgstr ""
"Uporabniški vmesnik temelji na paradigmi <ulink url=\"http://www."
"softpanorama.org/OFM/index.shtml\">Orthodox File Manager (OFM)</ulink>, 20 "
"let starem principu, ki je dokazal svojo kosti. Znan je kot preprost, "
"enostaven in močan. V naslednjih razdelkih bomo obravnavali osnovne funkcije "
"vsakega dela z izjemo:"

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <link linkend=\"menu-commands\">Menu Bar</link> which has a chapter of "
"its own."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"menu-commands\">Menijska vrstica</link>, ki ima svoje "
"poglavje."

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <link linkend=\"bookman\">Bookmarks</link> which has a chapter of its "
"own."
msgstr "<link linkend=\"bookman\">Zaznamki</link>, ki ima svoje poglavje."

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <emphasis role=\"bold\">Status Bar</emphasis> shows the properties of "
"the current file (that is being) in focus."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis role=\"bold\">Statusna vrstica</emphasis> prikazuje lastnosti "
"trenutne datoteke (ki je) v fokusu."

#. Tag: title
#: user-interface.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toolbars"
msgstr "Orodne vrstice"

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "&krusader; comes with several Toolbars."
msgstr "&krusader; prihaja z več orodnimi vrsticami."

#. Tag: title
#: user-interface.docbook:73 user-interface.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Main Toolbar</title>"
msgstr "<title>Glavna orodna vrstica</title>"

#. Tag: primary
#: user-interface.docbook:75 user-interface.docbook:112
#: user-interface.docbook:123 user-interface.docbook:145
#: user-interface.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toolbar"
msgstr "Orodna vrstica"

#. Tag: secondary
#: user-interface.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid "<secondary>Main Toolbar</secondary>"
msgstr "<secondary>Glavna orodna vrstica</secondary>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: user-interface.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Main Toolbar</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Glavna orodna vrstica</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &krusader; Main Toolbar is a standard &kde; toolbar that can be dragged "
"around the application (please unlock it first by unchecking the "
"<guimenuitem>Lock Toolbar Positions</guimenuitem> item in the right-click "
"menu) or configured via a <keycap>Right-Click</keycap> menu. You can decide "
"whether or not you want to display it each time you start &krusader; in the "
"<link linkend=\"konfigurator\">Konfigurator Startup page</link>, and you can "
"toggle its use in the current session in the <link linkend=\"settings-menu"
"\">Settings menu</link>. The Main Toolbar contents can be configured from "
"the <guimenuitem>Configure Toolbars...</guimenuitem> in the <link linkend="
"\"settings-menu\">Settings menu</link>. Since various commands and options "
"in &krusader; are context-dependent, some commands are not always available. "
"The icon of an inappropriate or inactive action will be deactivated (grayed-"
"out) disabling its use. <link linkend=\"bookman\">Bookmarks</link> can be "
"placed into the Main Toolbar and the Actions Toolbar with the mouse using "
"<quote>drag and drop</quote>."
msgstr ""
"&krusader; Glavna orodna vrstica je standardni &kde; orodno vrstico, ki jo "
"lahko vlečete po aplikaciji (najprej jo odklenite tako, da počistite polje "
"<guimenuitem>Zakleni položaje orodne vrstice</guimenuitem> v meniju z desnim "
"klikom) ali konfigurirate prek menija <keycap>Desni klik</keycap>. Odločite "
"se lahko, ali ga želite prikazati vsakič, ko zaženete &krusader; na <link "
"linkend=\"konfigurator\">strani za zagon Konfiguratorja</link>, njegovo "
"uporabo v trenutni seji pa lahko preklopite v <link linkend=\"settings-menu"
"\">meniju z nastavitvami</link>. Vsebino glavne orodne vrstice je mogoče "
"konfigurirati v <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj orodne vrstice...</guimenuitem> v "
"<link linkend=\"settings-menu\">meniju Nastavitve</link>. Ker različni ukazi "
"in možnosti v &krusader; so odvisni od konteksta, nekateri ukazi niso vedno "
"na voljo. Ikona neustreznega ali neaktivnega dejanja bo deaktivirana "
"(zasivljena), kar onemogoči njeno uporabo. <link linkend=\"bookman"
"\">Zaznamke</link> lahko postavite v glavno orodno vrstico in orodno vrstico "
"z dejanji z miško s <quote>povleci in spusti</quote>."

#. Tag: title
#: user-interface.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Job Toolbar</title>"
msgstr "<title>Orodna vrstica za delo</title>"

#. Tag: secondary
#: user-interface.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid "<secondary>Job Toolbar</secondary>"
msgstr "<secondary>Orodna vrstica za delo</secondary>"

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default, the &krusader; Job Toolbar (<link linkend=\"queue\">Queue "
"Manager</link> or simply the JobMan) is located at the right part of the "
"Main Toolbar. This toolbar allows you to view the job progress, to pause and "
"resume the job list execution and to undo the last executed job."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto je &krusader; Orodna vrstica Job (<link linkend=\"queue"
"\">Upravitelj čakalne vrste</link> ali preprosto JobMan) se nahaja na desnem "
"delu glavne orodne vrstice. Ta orodna vrstica vam omogoča ogled poteka "
"opravila, zaustavitev in nadaljevanje izvajanja seznama opravil ter "
"razveljavitev zadnjega izvedenega opravila."

#. Tag: title
#: user-interface.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Actions Toolbar</title>"
msgstr "<title>Orodna vrstica za dejanja</title>"

#. Tag: secondary
#: user-interface.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid "<secondary>Actions Toolbar</secondary>"
msgstr "<secondary>Orodna vrstica za dejanja</secondary>"

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"useractions\">UserActions</link> and <link linkend=\"bookman"
"\">Bookmarks</link> can be <quote>plugged</quote> into the <guilabel>Actions "
"Toolbar</guilabel>. To show it, use <menuchoice> <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Show Actions Toolbar</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> . To add user "
"actions, use <menuchoice> <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure "
"Toolbars...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> and select Actions Toolbar. You can, "
"for example, drag the Actions Toolbar to the right side using the mouse."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"useractions\">Uporabniška dejanja</link> in <link linkend="
"\"bookman\">Zaznamke</link> lahko <quote>priklopite</quote> v "
"<guilabel>Orodno vrstico z dejanji</guilabel>. Če ga želite prikazati, "
"uporabite <menuchoice> <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pokaži "
"orodno vrstico z dejanji</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> . Če želite dodati "
"uporabniška dejanja, uporabite <menuchoice> <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj orodne vrstice ...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> in "
"izberite Orodna vrstica dejanj. Z miško lahko na primer povlečete orodno "
"vrstico za dejanja na desno stran."

#. Tag: title
#: user-interface.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Location Toolbar</title>"
msgstr "<title>Orodna vrstica lokacije</title>"

#. Tag: secondary
#: user-interface.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid "<secondary>Location Toolbar</secondary>"
msgstr "<secondary>Orodna vrstica lokacije</secondary>"

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:148
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Below the <guibutton>Main Toolbar</guibutton> there is a <guibutton>Location "
"Toolbar</guibutton> for each panel. It shows the path the panel is currently "
"pointing to. When entering archives the path will be displayed in the "
"following format: <quote>archive type:/folder/archive_filename/the folder "
"inside the archive</quote>. This format makes the paths uniform and easy to "
"read. The <guibutton>Location Toolbar</guibutton> supports also KIO Slaves "
"but not all of them, some can only be used with the <link linkend=\"krviewer"
"\">viewer</link> and some can not be used. The user can enter a desired path "
"by clicking on it."
msgstr ""
"Pod <guibutton>Glavno orodno vrstico</guibutton> je <guibutton>Lokacijska "
"orodna vrstica</guibutton> za vsako ploščo. Prikazuje pot, na katero "
"trenutno kaže plošča. Pri vnosu arhivov bo pot prikazana v naslednji obliki: "
"<quote>vrsta arhiva:/mapa/ime_arhivske_datoteke/mapa znotraj arhiva</quote>. "
"Zaradi te oblike so poti enotne in enostavne za branje. "
"<guibutton>Lokacijska orodna vrstica</guibutton> podpira tudi podrejene KIO, "
"vendar ne vseh, nekatere je mogoče uporabljati le s <link linkend=\"krviewer"
"\">pregledovalnikom</link>, nekaterih pa ne. Uporabnik lahko vnese želeno "
"pot s klikom nanjo."

#. Tag: replaceable
#: user-interface.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid "/mnt/cdrom/"
msgstr "/mnt/cdrom/"

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput> <command>settings:/</command> </userinput>will browse and open "
"entries of the &systemsettings;."
msgstr ""
"<userinput> <command>nastavitve:/</command> </userinput>bo prebrskal in "
"odprl vnose v &systemsettings;."

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:178
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput> <command>trash:/</command> </userinput>opens trash folder."
msgstr ""
"<userinput> <command>smetnjak:/</command> </userinput>odpre mapo s smetnjaki."

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput> <command>mtp:/</command> </userinput>uses the kio_mtp to access, "
"upload and organize the multimedia stored on <trademark>Android</trademark>-"
"based devices."
msgstr ""
"<userinput> <command>mtp:/</command> </userinput>uporablja kio_mtp za "
"dostop, nalaganje in organiziranje večpredstavnosti, shranjene v napravah, "
"ki uporabljajo <trademark>Android</trademark>."

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"And last but not least <link linkend=\"remote-connections\">Remote "
"Connections</link> ."
msgstr ""
"In nenazadnje <link linkend=\"remote-connections\">Oddaljene povezave</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can copy-paste a &URL; in the <guibutton>Location Toolbar</guibutton> or "
"use a middle click. With the Right-Click menu you can configure the auto-"
"complete function. An optional <guilabel>Clear Location Toolbar</guilabel> "
"button is also available."
msgstr ""
"Lahko kopirate in prilepite &URL; v <guibutton>lokacijski orodni vrstici</"
"guibutton> ali uporabite srednji klik. Z menijem z desnim klikom lahko "
"konfigurirate funkcijo samodokončanja. Na voljo je tudi izbirni gumb "
"<guilabel>Počisti orodno vrstico lokacije</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Quick Navigation: &Ctrl; point with mouse in the middle of &URL; of the "
"<guibutton>Location Toolbar</guibutton>. A pop-up window shows the next "
"&URL; location. Pressing &Ctrl; + &LMB; shows the location where the mouse "
"was pointing to. This feature allows faster navigation in a big folder tree."
msgstr ""
"Hitra navigacija: &Ctrl; z miško pokažite na sredino &URL; "
"<guibutton>lokacijske orodne vrstice</guibutton>. Pojavno okno prikaže "
"naslednji &URL; lokacijo. S pritiskom &Ctrl; + &LMB; prikazuje lokacijo, "
"kamor je kazala miška. Ta funkcija omogoča hitrejšo navigacijo v velikem "
"drevesu map."

#. Tag: title
#: user-interface.docbook:210
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Panel Toolbar</title>"
msgstr "<title>Orodna vrstica plošče</title>"

#. Tag: secondary
#: user-interface.docbook:213
#, no-c-format
msgid "<secondary>Panel Toolbar</secondary>"
msgstr "<secondary>Orodna vrstica plošče</secondary>"

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each panel has a <link linkend=\"konfig-panel-buttons\">configurable Panel "
"Toolbar</link>. The complete Panel Toolbar or specific buttons can be made "
"visible or be hidden."
msgstr ""
"Vsaka plošča ima <link linkend=\"konfig-panel-buttons\">nastavljivo orodno "
"vrstico plošče</link>. Celotno orodno vrstico plošče ali določene gumbe "
"lahko naredite vidne ali skrite."

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:221
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>OpenDir Button</guibutton>: opens the folder browser."
msgstr "<guibutton>Gumb OpenDir</guibutton>: odpre brskalnik map."

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Equals Button (=)</guibutton>: changes the panel folder to the "
"other panel folder."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Gumb Equals (=)</guibutton>: spremeni mapo plošče v mapo druge "
"plošče."

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Up Button (..)</guibutton>: changes the panel folder to the "
"parent folder."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Gumb gor (..)</guibutton>: spremeni mapo plošče v nadrejeno mapo."

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Home Button (~)</guibutton>: changes the panel folder to the home "
"folder."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Gumb Domov (~)</guibutton>: spremeni mapo plošče v domačo mapo."

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Root Button (/)</guibutton>: changes the panel folder to the root "
"folder."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Korenski gumb (/)</guibutton>: spremeni mapo plošče v korensko "
"mapo."

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:246
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Sync-browsing Button</guibutton>: when active, each folder change "
"in the specific panel is performed in the other panel as well."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Gumb za sinhroniziranje brskanja</guibutton>: ko je aktiven, se "
"vsaka sprememba mape na določeni plošči izvede tudi na drugi plošči."

#. Tag: title
#: user-interface.docbook:255
#, no-c-format
msgid "Panels"
msgstr "Plošče"

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:256
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &krusader; panels are where most of the action takes place. Currently, "
"there are two types of panels:"
msgstr ""
"&krusader; na ploščah se odvija večina dogajanja. Trenutno obstajata dve "
"vrsti plošč:"

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:260
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"list_panel\">List Panel</link>: shows the files and folders."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"list_panel\">Plošča seznama</link>: prikazuje datoteke in "
"mape."

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:264
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"sidebar\">Sidebar</link>: has several display modes: "
"Preview, Tree, Quickselect, View and Disk Usage for the file or folder that "
"has the focus. The Sidebar may be left open or closed, as desired."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"sidebar\">Stranska vrstica</link>: ima več načinov prikaza: "
"predogled, drevo, hitra izbira, pogled in uporaba diska za datoteko ali "
"mapo, ki je v fokusu. Stransko vrstico lahko po želji pustite odprto ali "
"zaprto."

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:270
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&krusader; is a <quote>twin-panel</quote> file manager so there are two "
"panels: the <quote>Left</quote> panel and the <quote>Right</quote> panel, or "
"a more important logical distinction, the *Active* panel and the *Inactive* "
"panel. The active panel is the one that will accept your mouse and keyboard "
"input. If you choose a command from the <guilabel>Menu-Bar</guilabel> or "
"<guilabel>Toolbar</guilabel> the command will act upon the selected files/"
"folders in the active panel. You can switch between panels using the &Tab; "
"key or by clicking on the <guilabel>Information or Totals labels</guilabel>, "
"or by selecting any file in a panel with the mouse. As always, default "
"startup settings can be modified with the <link linkend=\"konfigurator"
"\">Konfigurator Startup page</link>, and you control the current session "
"with the <link linkend=\"settings-menu\">Settings menu</link>."
msgstr ""
"&krusader; je <quote>dvojni</quote> upravitelj datotek, tako da obstajata "
"dve plošči: <quote>leva</quote> plošča in <quote>desna</quote> plošča ali "
"pomembnejša logična razlika, Plošča *Aktivna* in plošča *Neaktivna*. Aktivna "
"plošča je tista, ki sprejme vaš vnos z miško in tipkovnico. Če izberete ukaz "
"v <guilabel>Menijski vrstici</guilabel> ali <guilabel>Orodni vrstici</"
"guilabel>, bo ukaz deloval na izbrane datoteke/mape v aktivni plošči. Med "
"ploščami lahko preklapljate z &Tab; ali s klikom na <guilabel>oznaki "
"Informacije ali Skupne vrednosti</guilabel> ali z izbiro katere koli "
"datoteke na plošči z miško. Kot vedno lahko privzete nastavitve zagona "
"spremenite na <link linkend=\"konfigurator\">strani za zagon Konfiguratorja</"
"link>, trenutno sejo pa nadzirate z <link linkend=\"settings-menu\">menijem "
"z nastavitvami</link >."

#. Tag: title
#: user-interface.docbook:287 user-interface.docbook:298
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>List Panel</title>"
msgstr "<title>Plošča s seznamom</title>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: user-interface.docbook:293
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>List Panel</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Plošče s seznamom</phrase>"

#. Tag: primary
#: user-interface.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid "Panel"
msgstr "Plošča"

#. Tag: secondary
#: user-interface.docbook:301
#, no-c-format
msgid "<secondary>List Panel</secondary>"
msgstr "<secondary>Plošča seznama</secondary>"

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:303
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the default panel and the one you will probably use most of the "
"time. This panel shows the contents of one folder which can be local (part "
"of your mounted file systems, either a native file or the files inside an "
"archive) or remote files (accessed via &FTP;, &NFS; or Samba). There are two "
"modes: <link linkend=\"view-menu\">Detailed View</link> that shows the file "
"names, file size, creation date and time and their attributes. And <link "
"linkend=\"view-menu\">Brief View</link> that shows only the file names, the "
"number of brief columns can be changed, by right clicking on the "
"<guilabel>Name</guilabel> header. File copy/paste/cut via clipboard between "
"&konqueror; and &krusader; <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>C</"
"keycap></keycombo>, <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>V</keycap></"
"keycombo>, <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>X</keycap></keycombo> "
"is supported. <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Ctrl; <keycap>R</keycap></"
"keycombo> toggles the <guilabel>List Panel</guilabel> between horizontal and "
"vertical mode."
msgstr ""
"To je privzeta plošča, ki jo boste verjetno uporabljali večino časa. Ta "
"plošča prikazuje vsebino ene mape, ki je lahko lokalna (del vaših nameščenih "
"datotečnih sistemov, izvorna datoteka ali datoteke v arhivu) ali oddaljene "
"datoteke (dostopne prek &FTP;, &NFS; ali Samba). Obstajata dva načina: <link "
"linkend=\"view-menu\">Podroben pogled</link>, ki prikazuje imena datotek, "
"velikost datoteke, datum in čas ustvarjanja ter njihove atribute. In <link "
"linkend=\"view-menu\">Kratek pogled</link>, ki prikazuje samo imena datotek, "
"število kratkih stolpcev lahko spremenite z desnim klikom na glavo "
"<guilabel>Ime</guilabel>. Kopiraj/prilepi/izreži datoteko prek odložišča med "
"&konqueror; in &krusader; <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>C</"
"keycap></keycombo>, <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>V</keycap></"
"keycombo>, <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>X</keycap></keycombo> "
"je podprt. <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Ctrl; <keycap>R</keycap></"
"keycombo> preklaplja <guilabel>podokno s seznamom</guilabel> med vodoravnim "
"in navpičnim načinom."

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:324
#, no-c-format
msgid "The following items are available:"
msgstr "Na voljo so naslednji elementi:"

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:327
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis> <guilabel>Information Label</guilabel> </emphasis>: shows how "
"much free space is physically available on the file system, the file system "
"capacity and where the filesystem is mounted. If the information is not "
"available (most often in the case of remote file system) a message will be "
"displayed with the reason for unavailability instead of the information."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis> <guilabel>Informacijska oznaka</guilabel> </emphasis>: prikazuje, "
"koliko prostega prostora je fizično na voljo v datotečnem sistemu, "
"zmogljivost datotečnega sistema in kje je datotečni sistem nameščen. Če "
"informacija ni na voljo (najpogosteje v primeru oddaljenega datotečnega "
"sistema), se namesto informacije izpiše sporočilo z razlogom nedostopnosti."

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:336
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>Media button</guibutton> on the left of the "
"<guilabel>Information Label</guilabel> displays a list of all available "
"media, where you can select the desired media (HDD partition, &DVD;, &USB; "
"stick, &etc;). Pressing <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>Return</keycap></keycombo> "
"when the <guibutton>Media menu</guibutton> is opened mounts the highlighted "
"media when it is unmounted, and unmounts it when it is mounted. The context "
"menu of a medium gives several options like <guilabel>Mount</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Open in a new tab</guilabel>, &etc; The <guibutton>Media menu</"
"guibutton> is <link linkend=\"konfig-panel-mediamenu\"> configurable</link>."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Gumb za medije</guibutton> na levi strani <guilabel>oznake z "
"informacijami</guilabel> prikaže seznam vseh razpoložljivih medijev, kjer "
"lahko izberete želeni medij (particijo trdega diska, &DVD;, &USB; ključ, "
"&etc;). Če pritisnete <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>Return</keycap></keycombo>, ko "
"je odprt <guibutton>meni Mediji</guibutton>, se označeni medij priklopi, ko "
"je odklopljen, in odpne, ko je priklopljen. Kontekstni meni medija ponuja "
"več možnosti, kot so <guilabel>Pripni</guilabel>, <guilabel>Odpri v novem "
"zavihku</guilabel> &etc; <guibutton>Meni Mediji</guibutton> je <link linkend="
"\"konfig-panel-mediamenu\"> nastavljiv</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:352
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis> <guilabel>Column Headers</guilabel> </emphasis>: here you can "
"change the sort order of the files and folders as desired. The default sort "
"order is by <guilabel>Name</guilabel>. The sort order can be instantly "
"changed by clicking on one of the <guilabel>Column Headers</guilabel>. To "
"reverse the sort order, click a second time on the Column Header. An arrow "
"will appear on the right of the Column Header text, showing the sort "
"direction (Up arrow = A to Z sorting, Down arrow = Z to A sorting). Default "
"<link linkend=\"useractions\">UserActions</link> set a keybinding for the "
"Column Headers. The default <guilabel>Column Headers</guilabel> are: "
"<guilabel>Name</guilabel>, <guilabel>Ext</guilabel>, <guilabel>Size</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Modified</guilabel>, <guilabel>rwx</guilabel>. "
"Predefined <link linkend=\"konfig-general\">Atomic extensions</link> like "
"<literal role=\"extension\">.tar.gz</literal> are shown as one part in the "
"<guilabel>Ext</guilabel> Column. More optional Column Headers are available "
"with the &RMB;. The width <guilabel>Column Headers</guilabel> can be changed "
"with the mouse by single clicking and moving the divider line to the desired "
"width (keep the mouse button pressed). Both <guilabel>List Panels</guilabel> "
"remember the sort order and column width. The <guilabel>Column Headers</"
"guilabel> can be changed and saved individually to each panel."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis> <guilabel>Glave stolpcev</guilabel> </emphasis>: tukaj lahko po "
"želji spremenite vrstni red datotek in map. Privzeti vrstni red razvrščanja "
"je po <guilabel>Imenu</guilabel>. Vrstni red lahko takoj spremenite s klikom "
"na eno od <guilabel>Glave stolpcev</guilabel>. Če želite obrniti vrstni red "
"razvrščanja, drugič kliknite glavo stolpca. Na desni strani besedila glave "
"stolpca se prikaže puščica, ki kaže smer razvrščanja (puščica navzgor = "
"razvrščanje od A do Ž, puščica dol = razvrščanje od Ž do A). Privzeta <link "
"linkend=\"useractions\">uporabniška dejanja</link> nastavijo vezavo tipk za "
"glave stolpcev. Privzete <guilabel>Glave stolpcev</guilabel> so: "
"<guilabel>Ime</guilabel>, <guilabel>Razširitev</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Velikost</guilabel>, <guilabel>Spremenjeno</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>rwx</guilabel>. Vnaprej določene <link linkend=\"konfig-general"
"\">Atomske razširitve</link>, kot je <literal role=\"extension\">.tar.gz</"
"literal>, so prikazane kot en del v stolpcu <guilabel>Ext</guilabel> . Več "
"izbirnih glav stolpcev je na voljo z &RMB;. Širino <guilabel>Glave stolpcev</"
"guilabel> lahko spremenite z miško z enim klikom in premikanjem ločilne črte "
"na želeno širino (pridržite miškino tipko). Obe <guilabel>Plošči s seznami</"
"guilabel> si zapomnita vrstni red in širino stolpca. <guilabel>Naslove "
"stolpcev</guilabel> je mogoče spremeniti in shraniti posamezno v vsako "
"ploščo."

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:385
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis> <guilabel>File List</guilabel> </emphasis>: displays the files "
"and folders in the browsed folder. The <link linkend=\"quicksearch\">search "
"bar</link> allows you to search for files by typing their names, or the "
"first few characters of a file name. Pressing &Enter; or double clicking on "
"a file will open/execute that file. You can select/unselect files using the "
"mouse, with the &Ins; key or the <link linkend=\"edit-menu\">Edit menu</"
"link>."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis> <guilabel>Seznam datotek</guilabel> </emphasis>: prikaže datoteke "
"in mape v brskani mapi. <link linkend=\"quicksearch\">Iskalna vrstica</link> "
"vam omogoča iskanje datotek tako, da vnesete njihova imena ali prvih nekaj "
"znakov imena datoteke. S pritiskom &Enter; ali dvojni klik na datoteko bo "
"odprl/izvedel to datoteko. Datoteke lahko izberete/prekličete izbor z miško, "
"z &Ins; tipko ali <link linkend=\"edit-menu\">meni Uredi</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:398
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis> <guilabel>Totals Label</guilabel> </emphasis>: selecting or "
"deselecting files will change the <emphasis> <guilabel>Totals Label</"
"guilabel> </emphasis>: selecting or deselecting files will change the "
"<emphasis> <guilabel>Totals Label</guilabel> </emphasis>at the bottom of the "
"panel, which displays how many files you have selected (and how much total "
"disk space they use) as well as the total file and disk usage of the current "
"folder (as opposed to the information label that displays information for "
"the whole file system). If a folder contains a lot of subfolders, it may not "
"be possible to drop the &URL; onto the panel (on which only folders are "
"visible), but the &URL; can be dropped onto the <quote>Information Label</"
"quote> or <quote>Totals Label</quote> instead. When a <link linkend=\"view-"
"menu\">custom filter</link> is set, it will show the setting, example: [*."
"cpp]."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis> <guilabel>Oznaka skupnih vrednosti</guilabel> </emphasis>: "
"izbiranje ali preklic izbire datotek bo spremenilo <emphasis> "
"<guilabel>Oznaka skupnih vrednosti</guilabel> </emphasis>: izbiranje ali "
"preklic izbire datotek bo spremenilo <emphasis> > <guilabel>Oznaka skupnih "
"vrednosti</guilabel> </emphasis>na dnu plošče, ki prikazuje, koliko datotek "
"ste izbrali (in koliko skupnega prostora na disku uporabljajo) ter skupno "
"uporabo datotek in diska trenutno mapo (v nasprotju z informacijsko oznako, "
"ki prikazuje informacije za celoten datotečni sistem). Če mapa vsebuje "
"veliko podmap, morda ne bo mogoče izpustiti &URL; na ploščo (na kateri so "
"vidne samo mape), vendar &URL; namesto tega lahko spustite na "
"<quote>Informacijsko oznako</quote> ali <quote>Skupno oznako</quote>. Ko je "
"nastavljen <link linkend=\"view-menu\">filter po meri</link>, bo prikazana "
"nastavitev, na primer: [*.cpp]."

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:418
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When using the <quote>&kde; default <link linkend=\"konfig-color\">colors</"
"link></quote>, then the selected files are shown in blue and the current "
"file is surrounded by a fine-lined rectangle. By default an icon is shown "
"according to the file type. Use <link linkend=\"konfig-panel\">Konfigurator "
"Panel page</link> to change the default configuration to meet your "
"individual needs."
msgstr ""
"Ko uporabljate <quote>&kde; privzete <link linkend=\"konfig-color\">barve</"
"link></quote>, potem so izbrane datoteke prikazane v modri barvi, trenutna "
"datoteka pa je obdana s pravokotnikom s finimi črtami. Privzeto je prikazana "
"ikona glede na vrsto datoteke. Uporabite <link linkend=\"konfig-panel"
"\">stran s ploščo konfiguratorja</link>, da spremenite privzeto "
"konfiguracijo, da ustreza vašim individualnim potrebam."

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:425
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some useful <guilabel>List panel</guilabel> <link linkend=\"key_bindings"
"\">Key-Bindings</link>:"
msgstr ""
"Nekaj uporabnih <guilabel>podokna s seznamom</guilabel> <link linkend="
"\"key_bindings\">Vezanja tipk</link>:"

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:429
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>R</keycap></keycombo> will refresh "
"the panel."
msgstr ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>R</keycap></keycombo> bo osvežil "
"ploščo."

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:435
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Focus a file or folder on the left panel, press <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl; &Right;</keycombo> and the right panel changes:"
msgstr ""
"Osredotočite se na datoteko ali mapo na levi plošči, pritisnite <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; &Right;</keycombo> in desna plošča se spremeni:"

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:441
#, no-c-format
msgid "On a file: the right panel gets the same path as the left panel."
msgstr "V datoteki: desna plošča dobi isto pot kot leva plošča."

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:445
#, no-c-format
msgid "On a folder: right panel opens the folder focused on the left panel."
msgstr "V mapi: desna plošča odpre mapo, ki je osredotočena na levo ploščo."

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:450
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For the right panel: press <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; &Left;</"
"keycombo> and the left panel will change."
msgstr ""
"Za desno ploščo: pritisnite <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; &Left;</"
"keycombo> in leva plošča se bo spremenila."

#. Tag: title
#: user-interface.docbook:458
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Sidebar</title>"
msgstr "<title>Stranska vrstica</title>"

#. Tag: primary
#: user-interface.docbook:460
#, no-c-format
msgid "<primary>Sidebar</primary>"
msgstr "<primary>Stranska vrstica</primary>"

#. Tag: secondary
#: user-interface.docbook:461
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sidebar (3rd Panel)"
msgstr "Stranska vrstica (3. plošča)"

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:463
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is <quote>&krusader; is 3rd Hand</quote> or the 3rd Panel, click on the "
"arrow-up button on the right of the <guilabel>Totals Label</guilabel> or "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt; &Down;</keycombo> to open the "
"<guilabel>Sidebar</guilabel>. This panel has several display modes which can "
"be activated by clicking on the appropriate button."
msgstr ""
"To je <quote>&krusader; je 3rd Hand</quote> ali 3rd Panel, kliknite gumb s "
"puščico navzgor na desni strani <guilabel>Oznaka skupnega zneska</guilabel> "
"ali <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt; &Down;</keycombo>, da odprete "
"<guilabel>stransko vrstico</guilabel>. Ta plošča ima več načinov prikaza, ki "
"jih lahko aktivirate s klikom na ustrezen gumb."

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:473
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis> <guilabel>Preview Panel</guilabel> </emphasis>: gives a preview "
"of the file that has the focus (currently selected file)."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis> <guilabel>Podokno za predogled</guilabel> </emphasis>: daje "
"predogled datoteke, ki je v fokusu (trenutno izbrana datoteka)."

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:480
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis> <guilabel>Tree Panel</guilabel> </emphasis>: is used to quickly "
"browse the local folder tree. This panel behaves like the list panel but "
"only one folder may be selected at a time and double clicking or pressing "
"&Enter; on a folder will open that folder in the active panel. The panels "
"fully support drag and drop (copy, move, link) mouse actions."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis> <guilabel>Drevesna plošča</guilabel> </emphasis>: uporablja se za "
"hitro brskanje po drevesu lokalnih map. Ta plošča se obnaša kot plošča s "
"seznami, vendar je naenkrat mogoče izbrati samo eno mapo in dvojni klik ali "
"pritisk &Enter; v mapi bo to mapo odprl v aktivni plošči. Plošče v celoti "
"podpirajo dejanja povleci in spusti (kopiraj, premakni, povezava)."

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:492
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis> <guilabel>Quick Panel</guilabel> </emphasis>: is used to quickly "
"select files, &eg; enter <literal role=\"extension\">*.png</literal> and "
"click on the <guibutton>Go</guibutton> button. The <quote>floppy</quote> "
"button stores the current selection. The <quote>select group dialog</quote> "
"is also available."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis> <guilabel>Hitra plošča</guilabel> </emphasis>: uporablja se za "
"hitro izbiro datotek, &eg; vnesite <literal role=\"extension\">*.png</"
"literal> in kliknite gumb <guibutton>Pojdi</guibutton>. Gumb <quote>disketa</"
"quote> shrani trenutno izbiro. Na voljo je tudi <quote>pogovorno okno za "
"izbiro skupine</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:503
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis> <guilabel>Viewer Panel</guilabel> </emphasis>: views a text file, "
"views an image, &etc; A thumbnail view is generated whenever you open the "
"<guilabel>Viewer Panel</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis> <guilabel>Podokno pregledovalnika</guilabel> </emphasis>: ogled "
"besedilne datoteke, ogled slike &etc; Pogled sličic se ustvari vsakič, ko "
"odprete <guilabel>Panel pregledovalnika</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:512
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis> <guilabel>Disk Usage Panel</guilabel> </emphasis>: views the "
"<link linkend=\"diskusage\">Disk Usage</link> of a folder."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis> <guilabel>Plošča za uporabo diska</guilabel> </emphasis>: prikaže "
"<link linkend=\"diskusage\">Uporabo diska</link> mape."

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:519
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is possible to change the sidebar placement using the rotation button "
"which is located to the left of the arrow down button at the bottom part of "
"the &krusader; tab. Each click on this button moves the sidebar on one "
"position in the loop <quote>bottom-left-top-right</quote>."
msgstr ""
"Postavitev stranske vrstice lahko spremenite z gumbom za vrtenje, ki se "
"nahaja levo od puščičnega gumba navzdol na spodnjem delu okna &krusader; "
"zavihek. Vsak klik na ta gumb premakne stransko vrstico na en položaj v "
"zanki <quote>spodaj-levo-zgoraj-desno</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:524
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If needed you can resize the window &eg; to better display a picture or view "
"a file contents. Click on the arrow down button to close the <guilabel>3rd "
"Hand Panel</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Po potrebi lahko spremenite velikost okna &eg; za boljši prikaz slike ali "
"ogled vsebine datoteke. Kliknite gumb s puščico navzdol, da zaprete "
"<guilabel>3rd Hand Panel</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: user-interface.docbook:530
#, no-c-format
msgid "Folder History"
msgstr "Zgodovina map"

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:531
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Both panels remember recently visited folders. Click on the "
"<guibutton>Folder history</guibutton> button (\"watch\" symbol) to open the "
"folder history list. Here you can quickly change to previously visited "
"folders. The currently focused folder is checked. On every new start of "
"&krusader;, the history list is populated by the items from previous run "
"(history is saved)."
msgstr ""
"Obe plošči si zapomnita nedavno obiskane mape. Kliknite gumb "
"<guibutton>Zgodovina mape</guibutton> (simbol \"watch\"), da odprete seznam "
"zgodovine map. Tukaj lahko hitro preklopite na predhodno obiskane mape. "
"Trenutno izbrana mapa je označena. Ob vsakem novem zagonu &krusader; se "
"seznam zgodovine napolni z elementi prejšnjega zagona (zgodovina se shrani)."

#. Tag: title
#: user-interface.docbook:541
#, no-c-format
msgid "Command Line / Terminal Emulator"
msgstr "Emulator ukazne vrstice/terminala"

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:542
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This part of the <link linkend=\"gloss-gui\">&GUI;</link> can have four "
"modes: Command Line, Terminal Emulator, show both and show none. You can "
"choose your mode of operation either on start-up with the <link linkend="
"\"konfigurator\">Konfigurator Startup page</link>, or for the current "
"session with the <link linkend=\"settings-menu\">Settings menu</link> ."
msgstr ""
"Ta del <link linkend=\"gloss-gui\">&GUI;</link> ima lahko štiri načine: "
"ukazna vrstica, terminalski emulator, prikaži oba in ne prikaži nobenega. "
"Način delovanja lahko izberete ob zagonu z <link linkend=\"konfigurator"
"\">strani za zagon konfiguratorja</link> ali za trenutno sejo z <link "
"linkend=\"settings-menu\">menijem z nastavitvami</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: user-interface.docbook:549 user-interface.docbook:552
#, no-c-format
msgid "Command Line"
msgstr "Ukazna vrstica"

#. Tag: phrase
#: user-interface.docbook:558
#, no-c-format
msgid "Command line"
msgstr "Ukazna vrstica"

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:562
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The traditional command line mode offers a single line of input to enter "
"commands, it also features three buttons:"
msgstr ""
"Tradicionalni način ukazne vrstice ponuja eno vrstico vnosa za vnos ukazov, "
"vsebuje pa tudi tri gumbe:"

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:566
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>command history</guibutton> (down arrow) to quick open previous "
"used commands"
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>zgodovina ukazov</guibutton> (puščica navzdol) za hitro odpiranje "
"prejšnjih uporabljenih ukazov"

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:571
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Useraction expander</guibutton> (green plus button) to add easy "
"<link linkend=\"useractions\">Useraction placeholders</link>"
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Razširjevalnik uporabniških dejanj</guibutton> (zeleni gumb plus) "
"za dodajanje enostavnih <link linkend=\"useractions\">oznak mest za "
"uporabniške akcije</link>"

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:577
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>run in terminal mode</guibutton> (console icon) button with the "
"next options:"
msgstr ""
"Gumb <guibutton>zagon v terminalskem načinu</guibutton> (ikona konzole) z "
"naslednjimi možnostmi:"

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:579
#, no-c-format
msgid "Start and Forget"
msgstr "Začni in pozabi"

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:582
#, no-c-format
msgid "Display Separated Standard and Error Output"
msgstr "Prikaz ločenega standardnega izhoda in izhoda napak"

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:585
#, no-c-format
msgid "Display Mixed Standard and Error Output"
msgstr "Prikaz mešanega standardnega izhoda in izhoda napak"

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:588
#, no-c-format
msgid "Start in New Terminal"
msgstr "Začnite v novem terminalu"

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:591
#, no-c-format
msgid "Send to Embedded Terminal Emulator"
msgstr "Pošlji v vgrajeni terminalski emulator"

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:601
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you start typing your commands, the command line auto-completion "
"feature will make its offers according to what you choose in the "
"&systemsettings;. If you want to change the way auto-complete behaves in the "
"current &krusader; session, <keycap>right click</keycap> on the command line "
"and change it. To the left of the input line you can find the local path "
"that the active panel is currently pointing to. This path is where your "
"command will be executed. Typing <userinput> <command>cd</command> "
"<replaceable> &lt;folder&gt;</replaceable> </userinput> in the command line "
"will also cause the active panel to point to this folder. Click <link "
"linkend=\"cmdline_keybindings\">here</link> to view the command line "
"keybindings."
msgstr ""
"Ko začnete vnašati svoje ukaze, bo funkcija samodokončanja ukazne vrstice "
"ponudila svoje ponudbe glede na to, kar izberete v &systemsettings;. Če "
"želite spremeniti način delovanja samodokončanja v trenutnem &krusader; "
"seje, <keycap>desni klik</keycap> na ukazno vrstico in jo spremenite. Na "
"levi strani vnosne vrstice najdete lokalno pot, na katero trenutno kaže "
"aktivna plošča. Na tej poti se bo izvršil vaš ukaz. Če v ukazno vrstico "
"vnesete <userinput> <command>cd</command> <replaceable> &lt;mapa&gt;</"
"replaceable> </userinput>, bo aktivna plošča pokazala na to mapo. Kliknite "
"<link linkend=\"cmdline_keybindings\">tukaj</link> za ogled povezav tipk "
"ukazne vrstice."

#. Tag: title
#: user-interface.docbook:624 user-interface.docbook:627
#, no-c-format
msgid "Terminal Emulator"
msgstr "Emulator terminala"

#. Tag: phrase
#: user-interface.docbook:633
#, no-c-format
msgid "Terminal emulator"
msgstr "Emulator terminala"

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:637
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The terminal emulator mode is in fact a small console and acts like one. You "
"can change the active folder in the terminal by using the <userinput> "
"<command>cd</command> </userinput> command. The terminal emulator will "
"follow the active panel folder. You can drag a file from the <interface>List "
"Panel</interface> and name of file will pasted into Terminal Emulator. If "
"you drag multiple files, the names will pasted into Terminal Emulator. A "
"full-screen terminal emulator can be used when <link linkend=\"konfig-"
"general-general\">configured</link> or <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; "
"&Shift;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo> toggles between normal and full screen "
"mode. If the command line is hidden, press <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; "
"<keycap>Arrow down</keycap></keycombo> to focus the terminal emulator. "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>Arrow up</keycap></keycombo> "
"brings you back down. <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Enter;</keycombo> "
"and <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; &Shift; &Enter;</keycombo> paste the "
"filename. You can close the emulator by typing <userinput> <command>exit</"
"command> </userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Način terminalskega emulatorja je pravzaprav majhna konzola in deluje kot "
"ena. Aktivno mapo v terminalu lahko spremenite z ukazom <userinput> "
"<command>cd</command> </userinput>. Emulator terminala bo sledil mapi "
"aktivne plošče. Datoteko lahko povlečete iz <interface>podokna seznama</"
"interface> in ime datoteke bo prilepljeno v terminalski emulator. Če "
"povlečete več datotek, bodo imena prilepljena v terminalski emulator. "
"Celozaslonski terminalski emulator je mogoče uporabiti, ko je <link linkend="
"\"konfig-general-general\">konfiguriran</link> ali <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl; &Shift;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo> preklaplja med običajnim in "
"celozaslonskim načinom. Če je ukazna vrstica skrita, pritisnite <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>Puščica navzdol</keycap></keycombo> za "
"fokusiranje terminalskega emulatorja. <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; "
"<keycap>Puščica navzgor</keycap></keycombo> vas vrne navzdol. <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Enter;</keycombo> in <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl; &Shift; &Enter;</keycombo> prilepite ime datoteke. Emulator lahko "
"zaprete tako, da vnesete <userinput> <command>exit</command> </userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:659
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click <link linkend=\"termemu_keybindings\">here</link> to view the Terminal "
"emulator keybindings."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite <link linkend=\"termemu_keybindings\">tukaj</link> za ogled povezav "
"tipk terminalskega emulatorja."

#. Tag: title
#: user-interface.docbook:667 user-interface.docbook:669
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Function (FN) Keys Bar</title>"
msgstr "<title>Vrstica s funkcijskimi tipkami (FN)</title>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: user-interface.docbook:675
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Function (FN) Keys Bar</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Vrstica s funkcijskimi tipkami (FN)</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:679
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This bar gets its name from the function (FN) keys it represents. For each "
"button on this bar there is a corresponding function key that performs the "
"same action. This bar is derived from the design of the first twin-panel "
"file managers and the FN keys usually act the same way with two changes: the "
"<keycap>F2</keycap> key is used to rename files and the <keycap>F9</keycap> "
"key will open a terminal at the last local path that the active panel "
"pointed to. <guilabel>Mkdir</guilabel> <keycap>F7</keycap> (translated name "
"of <command>mkdir</command> command) can create whole folder trees on the "
"fly &eg; <literal>foo/bar/test</literal>. You can choose to display <link "
"linkend=\"faqu_resize\">or not</link> the <guilabel>FN keys bar</guilabel> "
"when starting up &krusader; via the <link linkend=\"konfigurator"
"\">Konfigurator Startup page</link>, and you can toggle its use in the "
"current session with the <link linkend=\"settings-menu\">Settings menu</"
"link>. The actions and <link linkend=\"key_bindings\">Key-Bindings</link> "
"performed by the function keys are configurable since version 1.51, they "
"will remain active with or without the <guilabel>FN keys bar</guilabel> "
"displayed."
msgstr ""
"Ta vrstica je dobila ime po funkcijskih tipkah (FN), ki jih predstavlja. Za "
"vsak gumb v tej vrstici je ustrezna funkcijska tipka, ki izvaja isto "
"dejanje. Ta vrstica izhaja iz zasnove prvih upraviteljev datotek z dvema "
"ploščama in tipke FN običajno delujejo na enak način z dvema spremembama: "
"tipka <keycap>F2</keycap> se uporablja za preimenovanje datotek in tipka "
"<keycap>F9</keycap> bo odprla terminal na zadnji lokalni poti, na katero je "
"kazala aktivna plošča. <guilabel>Mkdir</guilabel> <keycap>F7</keycap> "
"(prevedeno ime ukaza <command>mkdir</command>) lahko sproti ustvarja celotna "
"drevesa map &eg; <literal>foo/bar/test</literal>. Izberete lahko, ali želite "
"prikazati <link linkend=\"faqu_resize\">ali ne</link> <guilabel>vrstico s "
"tipkami FN</guilabel> ob zagonu &krusader; prek <link linkend=\"konfigurator"
"\">strani za zagon Konfiguratorja</link>, njegovo uporabo v trenutni seji pa "
"lahko preklapljate z <link linkend=\"settings-menu\">menijem z nastavitvami</"
"link>. Dejanja in <link linkend=\"key_bindings\">Key-Bindings</link>, ki jih "
"izvajajo funkcijske tipke, je mogoče konfigurirati od različice 1.51, ostali "
"bodo aktivni z ali brez prikazane <guilabel>vrstice s tipkami FN</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: user-interface.docbook:702 user-interface.docbook:704
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Folder Tabs</title>"
msgstr "<title>Zavihki mape</title>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: user-interface.docbook:710
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Folder Tabs</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Zavihki mape</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:714
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With <guibutton>Folder Tabs</guibutton> you can quickly change to multiple "
"folders; each panel has its own <guibutton>Folder Tabs</guibutton>. The "
"<guibutton>Folder Tabs</guibutton> positions are saved when closing "
"&krusader;. To switch between <guibutton>Folder Tabs</guibutton>, click them "
"with the mouse. Squeezed <guibutton>Folder Tabs</guibutton> have tooltips to "
"display the full path. The following <guibutton>Folder Tabs</guibutton> "
"operations are available:"
msgstr ""
"Z <guibutton>Zavihki mape</guibutton> lahko hitro preklopite na več map; "
"vsaka plošča ima svoje <guibutton>Zavihke mape</guibutton >. Položaji "
"<guibutton>Zavihki mape</guibutton> se shranijo, ko zaprete &krusader;. Če "
"želite preklapljati med <guibutton>zavihki map</guibutton>, jih kliknite z "
"miško. Stisnjeni <guibutton>Zavihki mape</guibutton> imajo namige za prikaz "
"celotne poti. Na voljo so naslednje operacije <guibutton>Zavihki map</"
"guibutton>:"

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:724
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To <action>open a new tab</action> and keep the current tab opened: "
"<keycap>Right-click</keycap> on a folder and select <guimenuitem>Open in New "
"Tab</guimenuitem>, or click on the rightmost button on the Tab bar."
msgstr ""
"Če želite <action>odpreti nov zavihek</action> in obdržati trenutni zavihek "
"odprt: <keycap>Z desno tipko miške kliknite</keycap> na mapo in izberite "
"<guimenuitem>Odpri v novem zavihku</guimenuitem> ali kliknite na skrajni "
"desni gumb v vrstici z zavihki."

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:732
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To <action>lock a tab</action>, <keycap>Right-click</keycap> and select "
"<guimenuitem>Lock Tab</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite <action>zakleniti zavihek</action>, <keycap>kliknite z desno tipko "
"miške</keycap> in izberite <guimenuitem>Zakleni zavihek</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:736
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To <action>pin a tab</action>, <keycap>Right-click</keycap> and select "
"<guimenuitem>Pin Tab</guimenuitem>. The pinned tab is a locked tab but with "
"temporarily changeable address. It resets to pinned address on tab "
"reactivation. To unpin the pinned tab right-click on it and choose the "
"<guimenuitem>Unpin Tab</guimenuitem> item."
msgstr ""
"Če želite <action>pripeti zavihek</action>, <keycap>kliknite z desno miškino "
"tipko</keycap> in izberite <guimenuitem>Pripni zavihek</guimenuitem>. "
"Pripeti zavihek je zaklenjen zavihek, vendar z začasno spremenljivim "
"naslovom. Ob ponovni aktivaciji zavihka se ponastavi na pripet naslov. Če "
"želite odpeti pripeti zavihek, ga kliknite z desno tipko miške in izberite "
"element <guimenuitem>Odpni zavihek</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:740
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To <action>duplicate a tab</action>: <keycap>Right-click</keycap> on the "
"folder tab and select <guimenuitem>Duplicate Current Tab</guimenuitem>, or "
"use <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;&Alt;&Shift; <keycap>N</keycap></"
"keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite <action>podvojiti zavihek</action>: <keycap>Desni klik</keycap> na "
"zavihek mape in izberite <guimenuitem>Podvoji trenutni zavihek</guimenuitem> "
"ali uporabite <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;&Alt;&Shift; <keycap>N</"
"keycap></keycombo>."

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:750
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To <action>close a tab</action> (except for the last tab): <keycap>Right-"
"click</keycap> on the tab and select <guimenuitem>Close Current Tab</"
"guimenuitem>, or use the &MMB;, or use the Folder tab <guibutton>red cross</"
"guibutton> button, or use <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>W</"
"keycap></keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite <action>zapreti zavihek</action> (razen za zadnji zavihek): "
"<keycap>Desni klik</keycap> na zavihek in izberite <guimenuitem>Zapri "
"trenutni zavihek</guimenuitem> ali uporabite &MMB; , ali uporabite gumb "
"<guibutton>rdeči križ</guibutton> zavihka Mapa ali uporabite <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>W</keycap></keycombo>."

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:760
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To <action>change tabs</action>: <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>,"
"</keycap></keycombo> or <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>.</"
"keycap></keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite <action>spremeniti zavihke</action>: <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl; <keycap>,</keycap></keycombo> ali <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl; <keycap>.</keycap></keycombo>."

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:768
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To <action>open the current folder in a new tab</action>: use <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;&Alt;&Enter;</keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite <action>odpreti trenutno mapo v novem zavihku</action>: uporabite "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;&Alt;&Enter;</keycombo>."

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:773
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To <action>close all other tabs</action>, <keycap>Right-click</keycap> and "
"select <guimenuitem>Close Inactive Tabs</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite <action>zapreti vse druge zavihke</action>, <keycap>kliknite z "
"desno miškino tipko</keycap> in izberite <guimenuitem>Zapri neaktivne "
"zavihke</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:777
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To <action>close duplicated tabs</action>, <keycap>Right-click</keycap> and "
"select <guimenuitem>Close Duplicated Tabs</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite <action>zapreti podvojene zavihke</action>, <keycap>kliknite z "
"desno miškino tipko</keycap> in izberite <guimenuitem>Zapri podvojene "
"zavihke</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:781
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To move tab on the other panel, drag it to the area of the other panel with "
"the &LMB; (the mouse cursor will become an arrow pointing left or right) and "
"drop it. You can also press <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift; "
"<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite zavihek premakniti na drugi plošči, ga povlecite na območje druge "
"plošče z &LMB; (miškin kazalec bo postal puščica, ki kaže levo ali desno) in "
"ga spustite. Lahko tudi pritisnete <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift; "
"<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo>."

#. Tag: title
#: user-interface.docbook:789
#, no-c-format
msgid "Buttons"
msgstr "Gumbi"

#. Tag: para
#: user-interface.docbook:790
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Several buttons for fast operations are available: <link linkend="
"\"main_toolbar\">Main Toolbar</link>, <link linkend=\"actions_toolbar"
"\">Actions Toolbar</link>, <link linkend=\"panel_toolbar\">Panel Toolbar</"
"link>, <link linkend=\"location_toolbar\">Location Toolbar</link>, <link "
"linkend=\"list_panel\">Media</link>, <link linkend=\"folderhistory\">Folder "
"history</link>, <link linkend=\"bookman\">Bookmarks</link>, <link linkend="
"\"folder-tabs\">Tab</link>, <link linkend=\"cmdline\">Commandline</link>, "
"<link linkend=\"fnkeys\">Function keys</link>."
msgstr ""
"Na voljo je več gumbov za hitre operacije: <link linkend=\"main_toolbar"
"\">Glavna orodna vrstica</link>, <link linkend=\"actions_toolbar\">Orodna "
"vrstica dejanj</link>, <link linkend=\"panel_toolbar\">Orodna vrstica "
"plošče</link>, <link linkend=\"location_toolbar\">Orodna vrstica lokacije</"
"link>, <link linkend=\"list_panel\">Mediji</link>, <link linkend="
"\"folderhistory\">Zgodovina map</link>, <link linkend=\"bookman\">Zaznamki</"
"link>, <link linkend=\"folder-tabs\">Zavihek</link>, <link linkend=\"cmdline"
"\">Ukazna vrstica</link>, <link linkend=\"fnkeys\">Funkcija ključi</link>."
